{
  "stem": "24090.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Revulsion, horror, and I can't-- what-- what I can tell you is that I would read the Leon Uris book-- what was it-- And I was sick for a week afterwards because it could have been me.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was incomprehensible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I read Elie Wiesel's book, And it-- it stuck with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It has.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I can't-- I can't see those films about the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If I just hear the music on a little piece and-- on the television, I get sick to my stomach.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I have-- you mean my background and my culture-- culturally?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a big influence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With being associated with the Nazis?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I was a Jewish German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, that's different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's like an existential thing you're thrown into whatever is given you in life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My husband's background is Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he brought rich things from that culture through his Jewish mother, which I did through my Jewish mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She had marvelous values and things she taught me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We just happened to live in that country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were-- I mean, after all, the Jews were thrown from one country to another.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] So we're survivors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We do what we can.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't know how to explain that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It definitely had effects on me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't say it didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I know that I was fearful, protective, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did the best I could as a mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I really-- I think that also a part of being German is being somewhat perfectionistic and doing everything right.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But no one can.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I see things now I would do different possibly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I did the best I could.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
